title: NFL Week 7 Preview: How do QB injuries change playoff odds?
itunes:title: NFL Week 7 Preview: How do QB injuries change playoff odds?
description:
Cynthia Frelund and Matt "Money" Smith use predictive analytics to answer questions from Twitter, break down updated NFL playoff odds for teams facing QB injuries, preview a Super Bowl rematch between the New England Patriots and Atlanta Falcons (as well as every other game this week), and rank the NFC East QBs.
